      h2 THE STAR WARS STYLING
      markdown:
        ~~~ scss
        .emperor {
          @extend h1;
          text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .vador {
          @extend h2;
          font-weight: $font-weight-bold;
        }
        .maul {
          @extend h3;
          font-style: italic;
        }
        .sith {
          @extend h4;
        }
        .acolyte {
          @extend h5;
        }
